node.title: Person drowns at Wenderholm Regional Park
node.description: CPR was provided to them at the scene, but they couldn't be resuscitated.
node.content: ["Another person has drowned during New Zealand's summer holiday period, a police spokesperson has confirmed.", "At around 1:30pm a person was reported to emergency services as being unresponsive after getting into difficulty in the water at Wenderholm Regional Park in the Auckland region.", "\"CPR has been provided at the scene but unfortunately the person has died,\" the spokesperson said.", "No details have been given about the age or gender of the person.", "The death will be referred to the Coroner.", "It's the latest in a growing number of people dying in Aotearoa's water over the Christmas break period, including four dying in the Manawat\u016b River in Palmerston North.", "Emergency services are currently searching for a male swimmer in the Waingaro River, west of Ng\u0101ruaw\u0101hia."]
